About Us
Our History
A couple of college buddies who shared a passion for sports and cooking good food had a vision.  A sports bar!  But not just any sports bar. These guys worked their hardest to provide the ultimate game day experience in a family friendly atmosphere while offering the absolute biggest and best wings in town!
Today, Mr. Chubby's Wings has three locations where you can find great food, great service, great prices, and the best sports fans around.
Mr. Chubby's actively supports youth athletic programs in their communities so you can feel great about spending game day, or any other day, at your favorite neighborhood place.  So come on over and Chub it up!
